So he doesn't have enough ammunition to give you a flat tire.

23:26.032 --> 23:28.035
You just drove through a construction site.

23:28.515 --> 23:30.118
That's just weather.

23:30.719 --> 23:32.221
That's just life.

23:32.762 --> 23:34.905
That's just building materials.

23:35.666 --> 23:41.554
Some of the things that we are praying about at a warfare level, it's really just weather.

23:42.195 --> 23:46.821
Sometimes you don't need a three hour exorcism to get the spirit of depression out of your life.

23:47.302 --> 23:48.083
You need a walk.

23:49.145 --> 23:50.066
You need a walk.

23:50.754 --> 23:52.096
You need to get up and walk.

23:52.817 --> 23:54.439
Put your face up toward the sun.

23:54.499 --> 23:56.742
Let it beat on your face a little bit.

23:57.203 --> 23:58.925
Just get outside a little bit.

23:59.346 --> 24:00.808
Play a Bob Marley song.

24:01.108 --> 24:04.432
I don't know what it is, but sometimes it's just weather.

24:04.853 --> 24:09.439
Sometimes it's just the fact I told Holly, it had been five days since I left the house.

24:09.720 --> 24:11.462
Y'all, I love when it snows.

24:11.822 --> 24:13.104
I like to be by myself.

24:13.425 --> 24:14.546
It gives me an excuse.

24:14.606 --> 24:16.188
I can say I'm doing it out of safety.

24:16.529 --> 24:18.872
I'm really just doing it because I don't like to be around people.

24:19.272 --> 24:20.434
I really enjoy it.

24:21.442 --> 24:26.428
But you know, sometimes I'll get in this shutdown situation where I'll start thinking I'm under attack.

24:26.469 --> 24:27.290
I'm not under attack.

24:27.350 --> 24:28.311
I'm in isolation.

24:31.155 --> 24:38.865
And when I confuse what is warfare with what is weather, I'm trying to fight against everything in my life.

24:39.265 --> 24:41.168
And not everything is about a fight.

24:41.648 --> 24:43.611
Some things are just about a forecast.

24:44.893 --> 24:46.635
There are going to be good moods.

24:47.075 --> 24:49.138
There are going to be bad moods.

24:49.410 --> 24:53.695
There are going to be times that you come to church and you feel God.

24:54.416 --> 24:59.783
There are going to be sometimes when you come to church and you don't get anything resembling a goose bump.

25:00.504 --> 25:05.630
God is no less God when you didn't get a goose bump.

25:05.650 --> 25:10.556
God is not proven by goosebumps.

25:10.576 --> 25:11.397
You see what I'm saying?

25:12.579 --> 25:15.282
I feel like I can just break this down today a little bit.

25:16.898 --> 25:21.946
Because we think that naming the name of Jesus will cancel out the consequences of everyday life.

25:23.288 --> 25:26.433
Or that it's somehow going to make us float from one appointment to the other.

25:27.614 --> 25:28.856
Please don't believe this.

25:30.038 --> 25:37.229
One of the things that the Savior does so well in His teaching is that He prepares His disciples for the storm.

25:38.992 --> 25:41.115
I wish I would have told them to put one more scripture up there.

25:41.135 --> 25:45.001
I didn't think about using it, but I've been so good to see it.

25:45.041 --> 25:45.842
Mark chapter 8.

25:46.530 --> 25:46.710
22.

25:46.730 --> 26:01.028
Y'all were ready.

26:02.410 --> 26:05.133
They were more ready than I gave on credit for.

26:05.193 --> 26:10.099
Now, I really didn't tell them to put the Scripture up, but they were ready.

26:10.720 --> 26:14.024
When they came to Besay, actually, I want to go back a few verses before that.

26:14.044 --> 26:15.145
I want to go back to verse 14.

26:15.165 --> 26:15.826
Can y'all do that?

26:16.546 --> 26:23.814
when the disciples were in the boat with Jesus, and they had forgotten to bring bread except for one loaf they had with them in the boat.

26:24.695 --> 26:28.259
Be careful, Jesus warned them, watch out for the yeast of the Pharisees and that of Herod.

26:29.160 --> 26:31.503
They discussed this with one another and said, it's because we have no bread.

26:32.404 --> 26:35.267
Aware of their discussion, Jesus asked them, why are you talking about having no bread?

26:35.587 --> 26:39.852
Do you still not see or understand?

26:39.912 --> 26:42.855
Are your hearts hardened?

26:43.896 --> 26:45.298
Do you have eyes?

26:45.794 --> 26:46.716
but failed to see.

26:47.777 --> 26:50.381
And ears, but failed to hear.

26:50.422 --> 26:52.685
And don't you remember?

26:53.807 --> 26:58.575
When I broke the five loaves for the 5,000, how many basketballs of pieces did you pick up?

26:59.216 --> 27:00.398
12, they replied.

27:01.419 --> 27:05.226
And when I broke the seven loaves for the 4,000, how many basketballs of pieces did you pick up?

27:05.266 --> 27:06.848
They answered seven.

27:07.930 --> 27:12.818
He said to them, and this is what I want to ask myself sometimes, do you still not understand?

27:14.242 --> 27:20.031
Do you still not understand that just because you're not prepared doesn't mean God didn't provide?

27:21.994 --> 27:29.846
Do you not understand that just because the storm was sudden to you doesn't mean God stopped being sovereign over the storm?

27:31.930 --> 27:42.386
Don't you recognize that God who has called you by name will keep you through every season of your life?

27:43.138 --> 27:47.266
Now I don't know who this is for, but I want to minister to you because something has taken you by surprise.

27:48.749 --> 27:50.573
You did not expect that medical report.

27:51.375 --> 27:56.706
You did not expect to have to be in the principal's office keeping your kid in school every other week.

27:56.726 --> 28:00.914
You did not expect to still be doing fertility treatments three years into this journey.

28:01.410 --> 28:04.514
You did not expect to still be single in this season of your life.

28:04.914 --> 28:10.942
You did not expect for your marriage to be coming to an end at this young of a place in its inception.

28:11.282 --> 28:15.748
You did not expect to be this far behind in your finances at this age and stage.

28:16.208 --> 28:20.233
You did not expect to be this many years away from being able to retire.

28:20.554 --> 28:27.122
You did not expect to still be struggling with this issue that you have laid on the altar over and over.

28:27.234 --> 28:30.557
Again, you did not expect for the panic attacks to start again.

28:30.837 --> 28:32.198
They've been gone for three years.

28:32.659 --> 28:38.544
You did not expect for yourself to be reaching for the pills again because you thought you had moved on from that dependency.

28:38.904 --> 28:41.566
You did not expect that person to walk out of your life.

28:41.667 --> 28:45.850
In fact, they told you, I'll never leave you even if everybody else does.

28:46.331 --> 28:50.374
You did not expect in this season of your life to be feeling distant from God.

28:50.674 --> 28:57.220
You did not expect in this season of your life to feel so confused about what your next step is.

28:57.200 --> 29:01.064
remind you that you can be confidently confused.

29:03.066 --> 29:05.348
Confidently confused.

29:06.009 --> 29:15.359
That is, I did not expect this, but just because I wasn't prepared for this does not mean God hasn't provided for this.

29:16.039 --> 29:26.290
So now I'm just looking for the loaf that's in the boat that I did not see with my human eyes because I'm more ready than I recognize.

29:26.754 --> 29:33.382
Because if God put the crowd in front of me to feed, He will give me the bread to pass out in their hands.

29:33.983 --> 29:35.444
You understand what I'm saying?

29:35.484 --> 29:41.231
If God gave me the challenge to meet, God will give me the resource to meet it.

29:41.712 --> 29:43.614
Somebody say, I've got resource.

29:44.896 --> 29:46.217
I dare you to shout that again.

29:46.297 --> 29:47.398
I've got resource.

29:48.800 --> 29:53.746
Even if your bank account number says a different story, say, I've got resource.

29:54.402 --> 29:57.587
even if your cars in the shop say, I've got resource.

29:58.729 --> 30:03.116
I've got resource because number two, shout this, I've got relationship.

30:04.578 --> 30:11.409
Now anytime you've got relationship with somebody who's got resource, you've got resource.

30:12.271 --> 30:16.978
Anytime you've got relationship with somebody who is the source,

30:17.250 --> 30:28.869
You'll have to worry about the bread you forgot, or the mistake that you made, or the wrong turn that you took, or the stall-out that you've encountered, or the wisdom that you lack.

30:29.310 --> 30:36.982
If anyone lacks wisdom, let him ask to God who gives to all men liberally and operateeth not.

30:37.383 --> 30:39.186
So somebody say, I've got it.

30:39.970 --> 30:41.752
I don't feel it, but I've got it.

30:42.092 --> 30:43.854
I can't prove it, but I've got it.

30:44.154 --> 30:46.056
You can't see it, but I've got it.

30:46.456 --> 30:48.358
I'm not wearing it yet, but I've got it.

30:48.859 --> 30:50.680
I don't even feel it, but I've got it.

30:51.141 --> 31:02.351
And I'm practicing for where God is taking me because he's not done with me yet.

31:02.372 --> 31:04.694
I felt a little outline starting to form there.

31:05.174 --> 31:06.515
I've got resource.

31:07.156 --> 31:09.138
I've got relationship.

31:09.218 --> 31:16.246
Do you know what David did for his son Solomon when he was called to build the temple in 1 Chronicles, chapter 29?

31:16.606 --> 31:18.588
He got all the people together, right?

31:18.869 --> 31:20.130
The great King David.

31:20.411 --> 31:25.376
David got up in front of all the people and he said, my son is going to build a house for the Lord.

31:25.676 --> 31:28.199
It's going to be magnificent because God is.

31:28.560 --> 31:30.822
It's going to be great because God is.

31:31.243 --> 31:34.026
It's going to be spectacular because God is.

31:34.386 --> 31:37.810
It's going to be made of the best stuff because God is.

31:38.338 --> 31:39.259
And watch what he said.

31:39.279 --> 31:46.506
He said, my son Solomon, the one whom God has chosen is young and inexperienced and not ready.

31:48.769 --> 31:57.177
The task is great because this palatial structure is not for men, but for the Lord God with all my resources.

31:58.839 --> 32:00.360
I'm going to just preach this like I feel it.

32:02.102 --> 32:04.164
I saw a weird connection in the text.

32:04.264 --> 32:06.066
I did not expect this connection.

32:06.850 --> 32:20.205
But he said, with all my resource I have provided for the temple of my God, gold for the Goldberg, silver for the silver, bronze for the bronze, iron for the iron, and wood for the wood.

32:21.086 --> 32:26.572
So he's saying, I'm going to give my son something to work with.

32:26.592 --> 32:34.962
It's going to be gold for the gold work, silver for the silver work, bronze for the bronze work, iron for the iron work, and wood for the wood work.

32:35.554 --> 32:49.634
as well as onyx for the settings, turquoise, stones of various colors and all kinds of fine stone and marble, all of these in large quantities.

32:49.714 --> 32:55.642
He said, I'm going to give you everything you need to build because I know you don't feel ready yet.

32:57.225 --> 33:00.569
And you will have to work with it and you will have to form it and you will have to develop it.

33:00.910 --> 33:03.794
I hear the Lord saying to somebody, build with it.

33:05.634 --> 33:07.036
Build with it.

33:08.278 --> 33:09.580
Stop saying, I'm not ready.

33:09.600 --> 33:10.782
Stop saying, I don't have it.

33:11.202 --> 33:12.644
And build with it.

33:13.486 --> 33:18.333
You have resource because you have relationships.

33:18.353 --> 33:20.816
And David said, I have given it to my son.

33:20.837 --> 33:26.525
How much more will your father in heaven not give you everything you need for the season that you're in?

33:26.585 --> 33:29.830
Somebody received that word right now online.

33:30.751 --> 33:35.378
Repeat after me, I have everything I need.

33:35.842 --> 33:38.085
For the season, I'm in.

33:38.145 --> 33:46.336
Tell your neighbor you have everything you need for the season you're in.

33:46.396 --> 33:48.499
Tell them you have resource.

33:49.580 --> 33:51.202
Tell them you have relationship.

33:52.364 --> 33:54.507
Now somebody say, I've got resource.

33:55.828 --> 33:57.230
I've got relationship.

33:58.812 --> 34:00.114
I've got rocks.

34:05.890 --> 34:15.159
David said, I have stored up for my son Solomon everything he needs to build what God has called him to build.

34:16.280 --> 34:24.568
And one of the things he mentioned at the very end was precious stones or rocks.

34:25.569 --> 34:35.058
Now, if you remember anything about David, you know that a significant season of his life

34:35.618 --> 34:37.941
involved a rock.

34:39.382 --> 34:41.245
It was in precious stones.

34:41.845 --> 34:44.648
It was just a rock.

34:44.668 --> 34:48.673
As a matter of fact, I want to call Graham up to the stage right now.

34:49.294 --> 34:50.936
Give this boy a microphone.

34:51.436 --> 34:55.741
I did not prepare him for this, but give this boy a microphone.

34:56.282 --> 35:00.307
In his hand, I didn't talk to him about this, but he's ready.

35:00.707 --> 35:03.250
Graham, take them all the way up.

35:03.490 --> 35:18.091
to 1 Samuel 16 and tell them in 30 seconds the background of 1 Samuel 16, even though you weren't prepared to do this, I did not tell you to wear a sweater over a collared shirt.

35:18.412 --> 35:19.613
Watch God.

35:19.633 --> 35:25.682
I did not tell you to wear your best fit that you have worn in your entire teenage life.

35:25.794 --> 35:29.098
looking like a high school senior chosen by God.

35:29.459 --> 35:32.944
I just called you up here, and I gave you an assignment.

35:32.964 --> 35:42.316
Give us quickly the background of the man David from 1 Samuel 16 all the way up until he met Goliath, please, in 30 seconds.

35:42.637 --> 35:42.917
Go.

35:42.937 --> 35:46.943
1 Samuel 16, we got David, and he's just a shepherd boy.

35:46.983 --> 35:47.904
He's out in the field.

35:48.264 --> 35:49.426
His brothers are out.

35:49.506 --> 35:53.330
working in the military, and he's out there in the field taking care of the sheep.

35:53.370 --> 35:55.972
But one day this dude named, what is his name?

35:55.992 --> 35:56.713
The Prophet came.

35:57.013 --> 35:57.614
He pulled up.

35:57.694 --> 35:59.456
He was like, yo, Samuel.

35:59.516 --> 36:00.236
Samuel pulled up.

36:00.277 --> 36:02.078
He was like, yo, God wants a king.

36:02.098 --> 36:03.279
It's going to be one of y'all.

36:03.319 --> 36:04.320
They lined them up.

36:04.340 --> 36:05.482
It was none of the older brothers.

36:05.602 --> 36:07.844
They were like, we got the younger brother, David.

36:08.224 --> 36:08.925
David pulled up.

36:09.285 --> 36:10.547
He was like, yo, you're going to be the king.

36:10.587 --> 36:11.728
David came.

36:11.768 --> 36:13.790
David was the king, but he had to go back out to the field.

36:14.090 --> 36:14.651
So he's a king.

36:14.671 --> 36:15.271
He's in the field.

36:15.291 --> 36:16.592
He's got oil, but he's in the field.

36:16.953 --> 36:18.194
And then one day,

36:18.274 --> 36:25.225
One day, this giant named Goliath pulled up to the front lines of the military, and he was taunting them.

36:25.266 --> 36:26.888
He was saying, where's your God?

36:26.908 --> 36:27.750
You guys are weak.

36:27.810 --> 36:28.311
What the heck?

36:28.351 --> 36:30.634
Someone said, someone come 1v1 me.

36:30.654 --> 36:31.356
We're going to run it.

36:31.836 --> 36:34.120
If you win, then your God's real, whatever.

36:34.160 --> 36:36.444
They're like, I don't know who it's going to be.

36:36.865 --> 36:42.514
But then David, his dad told him, yo, go deliver these cheese pizzas to your brothers.

36:42.690 --> 36:44.992
They're in the military, they need the cheese pizzas.

36:45.353 --> 36:59.046
So David, with a good attitude, he woke up early, and he ran to his brothers in the field, and he pulled up, and he saw the giant standing on the front lines, and he was like, who is this guy to be taunting and making fun of my God?

36:59.326 --> 37:02.209
And why are you guys standing back there and not doing anything about it?

37:04.912 --> 37:08.595
And his brothers got mad at him, they were like, bro, who are you pulling up?

37:08.615 --> 37:11.218
Ah, which brings me?

37:12.162 --> 37:14.084
to 1 Samuel 1733.

37:14.885 --> 37:18.189
And David said, I'll kill him.

37:19.050 --> 37:24.437
And Saul replied, you are not able to go out against this Philistine and fight him.

37:24.798 --> 37:26.580
You are only a young man.

37:26.640 --> 37:29.964
And he has been a warrior from his youth.

37:30.064 --> 37:34.710
So Saul said, you're not ready for Goliath.

37:34.730 --> 37:41.458
And David said, nah, Goliath isn't ready for me.

37:41.922 --> 37:51.602
But David said to Saul, your servant has been keeping his father seated.

37:52.002 --> 37:57.689
When a lion or a bear came and carried off a sheep from the flock, I was practicing.

37:58.150 --> 37:59.111
I went after it.

37:59.531 --> 38:00.332
I struck it.

38:00.773 --> 38:01.954
I've been practicing.

38:02.335 --> 38:03.256
I've been working.

38:03.716 --> 38:04.617
I've been praying.

38:05.178 --> 38:06.099
I've been praising.

38:06.500 --> 38:07.481
I've been studying.

38:07.881 --> 38:08.903
I've been sinking.

38:09.343 --> 38:11.145
I've been on my spot.

38:11.165 --> 38:12.968
I've been on my post.

38:12.988 --> 38:14.209
I've been in my bag.

38:14.670 --> 38:16.292
I've been in my field.

38:16.312 --> 38:18.134
I've been in my anointing.

38:18.154 --> 38:19.976
I've been in my row.

38:19.996 --> 38:21.458
I've been doing that.

38:22.530 --> 38:23.371
Give me the verse.

38:25.574 --> 38:26.515
I went after it.

38:26.855 --> 38:35.867
I struck it, and I rescued the sheep from its mouth, and when it turned on me, I seized it by its hair, and I struck it, and I killed it.

38:36.307 --> 38:51.346
And your servant has killed both the lion and the bear, this uncircumcised Philistine, this fear, this insecurity, this addiction, this generational curse, this storm, this Philistine.

38:51.458 --> 38:56.325
will be like one of them because he has defied the armies of the living God.

38:56.385 --> 39:04.936
The Lord who rescued me from the Paul the lion and the Paul the bear will rescue me from the hand of this Philistine.

39:05.337 --> 39:06.458
I've been practicing.

39:06.819 --> 39:10.444
Saul said to David, go and the Lord be with you.

39:10.784 --> 39:12.266
And David said, that's right.

39:12.727 --> 39:18.755
I'm more ready than you recognize because I look like a shepherd, but I'm really a king.

39:18.775 --> 39:20.818
I look like a boy.

39:20.962 --> 39:24.126
But I'm really a bad man.

39:25.108 --> 39:28.052
I'm a bad dude.

39:28.072 --> 39:28.873
Next verse.

39:29.254 --> 39:32.158
Then Saul dressed David in his own tunic.

39:32.178 --> 39:36.183
He put a coat of armor on him and a bronze helmet on his head.

39:36.544 --> 39:42.192
And David fastened his sword over the tunic and tried walking around because he was not used to them.

39:42.612 --> 39:43.854
I cannot go in these.

39:43.894 --> 39:46.157
He said to Saul, because I'm not used to them.

39:46.217 --> 39:47.940
So he took them off.

39:48.000 --> 39:49.682
Then he took his staff.

39:49.762 --> 39:59.696
in his hand chose five smooth stones from the stream.

40:01.158 --> 40:09.550
Put them in the pouch of his shepherd bag and with his sling in his hand approached the Philistines.

40:10.011 --> 40:12.334
The only thing wrong with David is he was wasteful.

40:12.915 --> 40:14.898
Four of those stones were unnecessary.

40:18.530 --> 40:25.779
So what I'm trying to say to you today in a way that maybe you can apply to your life is you've got a rock.

40:32.488 --> 40:36.393
And you're more ready than you recognize.

40:37.855 --> 40:43.402
I would not have called him up here if I were not confident he could do it.

40:45.425 --> 40:46.546
The calling

40:46.978 --> 40:48.501
proves my confidence.

40:49.903 --> 40:55.192
God would not call you to do it if he was not confident that you could.

40:55.232 --> 41:00.381
Why am I confident that he can do it?

41:00.902 --> 41:12.402
Because he's been practicing this sermon because he was going to preach it this Sunday night to his Bible study, but it's going to get canceled because of the storm.

41:13.762 --> 41:31.969
But God knew before the storm was announced on the Weather Channel that I would need an illustration in this moment so God gave him the word to bring into this situation for your life today so I could let you know you've got a rock.

41:33.010 --> 41:34.072
You've got a rock.

41:35.234 --> 41:36.576
What did Jesus say?

41:36.616 --> 41:43.666
Everyone who hears these words of mind is like a wise man who built his house

41:43.938 --> 41:45.540
on the rock.

41:46.080 --> 41:48.003
I got a rock when the wind blows.

41:48.503 --> 41:50.505
I got a rock when the rain comes.

41:50.946 --> 41:53.088
I got a rock when the flood rises.

41:53.529 --> 41:56.372
I got a rock when the doctor says I won't live.

41:56.893 --> 41:59.315
I got a rock with a learning disability.

41:59.776 --> 42:01.638
I got a rock when they fire me.

42:02.058 --> 42:04.541
I got a rock when the storm comes.

42:07.625 --> 42:08.946
Because I've got a God.

42:09.570 --> 42:22.507
who is not only above my storm, but he is the crown beneath my feet on Christ, the solid rock.

42:22.527 --> 42:23.168
I stand.

42:24.710 --> 42:29.277
All other ground is sinking.

42:33.382 --> 42:36.306
How you been building your house?

42:37.634 --> 42:38.054
You're good.

42:38.275 --> 42:39.175
You preached better than me.

42:39.195 --> 42:39.856
Get off the stage.

42:39.896 --> 42:40.977
Just make me intimidated.

42:43.460 --> 42:45.722
He was ready.

42:45.742 --> 42:46.362
He was ready.

42:51.888 --> 42:52.528
And so are you.

42:55.091 --> 42:55.551
So are you.

42:55.771 --> 42:56.732
You're more ready than you.

42:59.395 --> 42:59.915
Realize.

43:01.857 --> 43:03.379
You're more ready than you recognize.

43:04.700 --> 43:06.802
You're more ready than you feel like you are.

43:07.234 --> 43:13.704
Have you been building your house on the sand of situations and circumstances?

43:15.386 --> 43:20.754
Have you been running around all the devils attacking me, trying to do warfare where it's really just weather?

43:23.559 --> 43:25.962
This is not some proof that you're not in the will of God.

43:26.823 --> 43:28.947
It's just proof that you are on planet Earth.

43:30.930 --> 43:31.531
It's weather.

43:33.213 --> 43:33.874
It's weather.

